OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry end to
OL,6,Fthe afternoon with clear spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping widely this evening. Cloud
OL,8,Fbuilding overnight but staying dry
OL,9,Fwith light winds. Turning chilly with
OL,10,Fa touch of frost possible in rural
OL,11,Fspots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA largely cloudy morning on
OL,14,FFriday with patchy outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fand drizzle pushing across the region
OL,16,Fduring the day. Strengthening winds,
OL,17,Fthese becoming gusty overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
